Pwede ka ihatid ng guard ko pauwi.

00:40:08.220 --> 00:40:09.260
Salamat, Ginoong Jiang Ling.

00:40:11.260 --> 00:40:12.100
Paalam.

00:40:13.340 --> 00:40:14.180
Teka.

00:40:16.320 --> 00:40:18.300
Ginoong Jiang Ling,
